snippet.title: Xenogunner Returns - 15 second gameplay clip (SAGE 2024 submission archive)
snippet.description: This is the 15 seconds of footage that were submitted to SAGE 2024, for the purpose mostly of archival but also to give people a short demonstration of the game. There is no sound in this footage.
